      "gear_destroyed": true,
      "constraints": [
        "rune must be at s:0 (any upgraded rune blocks recycle for that gear)"
      ],
      "_bulk_recycle_note": "The game also has a 3-gear bulk recycle that yields 1-3 RNG bonus runes on top of returning attached s:0 runes. That bonus path is a generic gear-recycling reward outside the advisor's planning scope and is intentionally NOT modeled in v1 — players can opt into it themselves once the advisor's targeted recycle steps are done."
